# gt-to-lt

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `commutativity_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (gt ?x ?y)
rhs: (lt ?y ?x)
